data.description: Beautiful and Charming 2 bedroom home. Great for first time buyer, comes with a spacious backyard, privately enclosed with cinder block walls. 2- Car detached garage. Has nice space for entertaining. Privately fenced front yard. Well kept interior recently painted. Saltillo type flooring throughout. Home is cozy and spotless. Within close proximity to Sofi Stadium home to Los Angeles Rams, the Los Angeles Chargers...and concession  many big entertainment events, LAX, Hollywood park casino, shopping centers, restaurants, and schools.
